text: Dune 2000 is a real-time strategy game released by Westwood Studios. It based on Frank Herbert's Dune. It uses a similar game engine to Command & Conquer: Red Alert. == Houses == Like in Dune II, the three main playable housess are House Atreides, House Harkonnen and House Ordos. Category:1998 video games
title: Dune 2000
